        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Infectious Disease Epidemic and Pandemic Preparedness Act</b></p> <p>This bill establishes the National Medical Command and a grant program within the Department of Health and Human Services to prevent and respond to infectious diseases. It also requires a strategic plan focused on treatments and vaccine development for infectious diseases.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
